[I] A Paradroid clone

[T] THE CLASSICAL FREEDROID: Freedroid is a clone of the classic game
[T] "Paradroid" on Commodore 64 with some improvements and extensions to
[T] the classic version.
[T]
[T] In this game, you control a robot, depicted by a small white ball with
[T] a few numbers within an interstellar spaceship consisting of several
[T] decks connected by elevators.
[T]
[T] The aim of the game is to destroy all enemy robots, depicted by small
[T] black balls with a few numbers, by either shooting them or seizing
[T] control over them by creating connections in a short subgame of
[T] electric circuits.

[U] https://freedroid.sourceforge.net

[A] Johannes Prix <johannesprix@users.sourceforge.net>
[A] Reinhard Prix <rprix@users.sourceforge.net>

[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/game
#[C] extra/game/rpg

